OL,3,CUK to develop underwater drones with
OL,4,CAustralia and US
OL,6,FITV News Asia Correspondent Debi
OL,7,FEdward explains the significance of
OL,8,Fthe Aukus partnership's announcement
OL,9,Fof its unmanned undersea drone project
OL,11,FBritain, Australia and the US have
OL,12,Fannounced the next step in their Aukus
OL,13,Fdefence partnership with an agreement
OL,14,Fto produce kit for underwater military
OL,15,Fdrones.
OL,17,FDefence Secretary John Healey said the
OL,18,Fdrones would form part of the UK's so-
OL,19,Fcalled new "hybrid navy" as Britain
OL,20,Fseeks to bolster its fleet with the
OL,21,Flatest cutting-edge technologies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780265472
OL,3,CUK to develop underwater drones with
OL,4,CAustralia and US
OL,6,FThe agreement involves developing new
OL,7,Ftechnologies such as weapons and
OL,8,Fsensors that can be deployed from
OL,9,Funderwater drones, known as uncrewed
OL,10,Funderwater vehicles (UUVs).
OL,12,FHealy announced the project alongside
OL,13,Fhis US counterpart Pete Hegseth and
OL,14,FAustralian deputy prime minister
OL,15,FRichard Marles at a defence conference
OL,16,Fin Singapore.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780265472
OL,3,CUK to develop underwater drones with
OL,4,CAustralia and US
OL,6,F"Together we are announcing ground-
OL,7,Fbreaking underwater capabilities that
OL,8,Fwill keep Britain safe, backing
OL,9,FBritish businesses that are driving
OL,10,Fgrowth, and standing shoulder to
OL,11,Fshoulder with our closest allies,"
OL,12,FHealy said.
OL,14,F"This is what modern defence looks
OL,15,Flike. We're stepping on the
OL,16,Faccelerator to develop cutting-edge
OL,17,Ftech to boost our collective
OL,18,Fdeterrence and support our shared
OL,19,Fsecurity."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@bO]vD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
