OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780265472
OL,3,CUK to develop underwater drones with
OL,4,CAustralia and US
OL,6,FThe project is expected to deliver its
OL,7,Ffirst equipment as early as next year,
OL,8,Fas the Royal Navy looks to move
OL,9,Ftowards a "hybrid" model featuring
OL,10,Fgreater use of drones.
OL,12,FThat move has already seen the Navy
OL,13,Finvest in uncrewed minehunters, which
OL,14,Fhave been loaded onto the support ship
OL,15,FRFA Lyme Bay for a possible deployment
OL,16,Fto the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,26,@qD@KOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780265472
OL,3,CUK to develop underwater drones with
OL,4,CAustralia and US
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Defence said the new
OL,7,Ftechnology would allow the Royal Navy
OL,8,Fto detect underwater threats to subsea
OL,9,Finfrastructure, such as internet
OL,10,Fcables in the North Sea that have
OL,11,Frecently been the target of Russian
OL,12,Fspy ships.
OL,14,FSaturday's agreement in Singapore is
OL,15,Fthe first project announced under
OL,16,F"pillar 2" of the Aukus defence
OL,17,Fagreement signed between the UK,
OL,18,FAustralia and the US in 2021.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
