FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780265472
OL,3,CUK to develop underwater drones with
OL,4,CAustralia and US
OL,6,FPillar 2 involves co-operation between
OL,7,Fthe three nations on cutting-edge
OL,8,Fmilitary technology, while "pillar 1"
OL,9,Fis a deal to provide Australia with
OL,10,Fnuclear-powered submarines.
OL,12,FIt comes a month after the Commons
OL,13,FDefence Committee warned pillar 2 was
OL,14,Fyet to deliver on its promise and was
OL,15,Frunning out of time to retain its
OL,16,F"credibility".
OL,26,@pD@\OUpD@eO]xD@AOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
