FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780265472
OL,3,CUK to develop underwater drones with
OL,4,CAustralia and US
OL,6,FOn Saturday, the three politicians
OL,7,Falso announced that a US nuclear-
OL,8,Fpowered submarine would visit
OL,9,FAustralia in 2027 as part of Aukus's
OL,10,F"Submarine Rotational Force-West" ` a
OL,11,Fcommitment by the UK and US to provide
OL,12,Fa submarine presence at Australia's
OL,13,FPerth naval base.
OL,15,FIt follows a visit by the UK's HMS
OL,16,FAnson attack submarine to the base
OL,17,Fearlier this year for a maintenance
OL,18,Fperiod that was reportedly cut short
OL,19,Fdue to the outbreak of the Iran war.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@aO]
